{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"38960be5e2","title":"毛泽东对八届八中全会《为保卫党的总路线、反对右倾机会主义而斗争》决议稿的批语和修改时部分加写的话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"49cd742355","index":0,"year":1959,"month":8,"day":2,"articleId":"38960be5e2"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"45d7403c51","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对八届八中全会《为保卫党的总路线、反对右倾机会主义而斗争》决议稿的批语和修改时部分加写的话","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"2bf408cd39","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"827335fc37","type":"paragraph","text":"送乔木同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"17e0f9730b","type":"paragraph","text":"有一点修改，请你们斟酌。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"ef3b943355","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东八月二日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"1882ca23df","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"9741f69ddf","type":"appellation","text":"即送陈伯达、王稼祥、胡乔木三位同志：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"abb6dcaadd","type":"paragraph","text":"加了一段，认为有必要，不知你〔们〕以为然否?请你们讨论一次。有小部分的分析及字句，与(四)节重复，如何调整一下，亦请斟酌。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"5ab7d6d742","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东八月六日九时","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"a22588fa0b","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"807fced5db","type":"paragraph","text":"尚昆同志：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"aa572a66fa","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请印20份，发常委，彭真，伯达、稼祥、乔木，七个大区组长及曾希圣。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"6e96936837","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东八月八日","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"5b4496989d","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"791a06a3bd","type":"paragraph","text":"我国现在还处在由资本主义到社会主义的过渡时期。阶级依然存在。对于旧的社会经济制度虽已基本上改造完成，但是尚未彻底完成。资本家还拿定息。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"f40c8ca8ec","type":"subtitle","text":"五","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"42b75aa323","type":"paragraph","text":"城乡资产阶级反动的思想活动和政治活动，虽经一九五七年整风反右斗争给了一次决定性的打击，但是还远没有彻底消灭。他们的反动的思想活动和政治活动，在一部分富裕中农和知识分子中间尚有市场，一遇风吹草动，他们就要蠢动起来。总之，资产阶级残余的思想政治活动既然存在，就一定会在共产党内找到他们的代表人物。而现在果然出了一小批(在中央委员会内是四个人)代表他们说话的党内的右倾机会主义分子。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"3932aa272f","type":"subtitle","text":"六","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"},{"id":"62ee67cfe4","type":"paragraph","text":"一部分共产党人的悲观主义思潮，右倾机会主义思潮，是社会上资产阶级反社会主义思潮在党内的反映。在由资本主义到社会主义的过渡时期，无产阶级同资产阶级的思想政治斗争，是波浪式的，高一阵，低一阵，再高一阵，再低一阵，直到这一场斗争彻底熄灭为止，那就是资产阶级思想政治影响最后消灭的时候。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2"}],"page":{"id":"2d7d8d3e43","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38960be5e2","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}